===dNetHack===
In [[dNetHack]], [[notdNetHack]] and [[notnotdNetHack]], there are three separate monster classes for angels and minions of each alignment. Lawful angels and minions consist of the angelic beings from ''NetHack'' alongside several other monsters, and both lawful and neutral angels and minions use different glyphs - chaotic angels and minions retain the {{white|A}} glyph.

The three alignments of angelic being or minion are listed below:

* [[Lawful angels and minions]]
* [[Neutral angels and minions]]
* [[Chaotic angels and minions]]

